<p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 1.1pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 18.4pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21.7pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">为全面贯彻党的二十大精神，认真落实习近平总书记关于教育的重要论述和视察江西重要讲话精神，紧紧围绕立德树人根本任务，深入贯彻实践育人理念，突出职业型人才培养，不断提高人才培养质量，切实做好学校</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">2024届毕业生就业工作，促进毕业生高质量充分就业。10月27日上午，“江西软件职业技术大学专场招聘会暨2023年湾里管理局秋季“百场校招”&nbsp;启动仪式活动”在学校田径场隆重举行</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">。</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">本次参会企业共</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">150余家</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">。</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">广州赣之韵科技有限公司、南昌金友科技有限公司、上海煦日网络科技有限公司等</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">20余家校友企业参加了招聘会，为我校在校生提供了岗位数500多个。涵盖了软件工程、电子商务、网络工程、教育、传媒等多个行业，为促进2024届毕业生高质量充分就业提供了坚实的保障。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 1.1pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 18.4pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21.7pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 1.1pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 18.4pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21.7pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-11-01%2016%3A02%3A40640%20%281%29.jpg?Expires=2014185760&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=3Qkfr5jaemCuBDPY9Bi8VVXFsCY%3D" alt="" width="650" height="488" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 1.1pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 18.4pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21.7pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 1.1pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 18.4pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 22.85pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">会场气氛热烈，同学们手持自己精心准备的简历，积极与招聘人员交流，主动了解用人单位的情况。校友们与毕业生热情互动，校友企业仔细询问毕业生的就业意向，毕业生也对就业市场有了较为清晰的认识。部分校友企业还在相关学院举办了专场宣讲会。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 1.1pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 18.4pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 22.85pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 1.1pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 18.4pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 22.85pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-11-01%2016%3A03%3A26640.jpg?Expires=2014185806&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=Lm6AanfSslzMGJ7WVlSooP9FQBY%3D" alt="" width="650" height="488" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 1.1pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 18.4pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 22.85pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 1.1pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21.7pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">校党委书记江延湖、执行校长范红铭、副校长张永革亲临招聘现场指导工作，在校长助理、校友联络办公室主任夏光辉的陪同下看望各地返校参会的校友代表，亲切询问了解各企业目前的发展现状和人才需求，并对校友返校助力母校就业工作表示感谢。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">本次招聘会的成功举办，架起了毕业生与校友企业之间沟通的桥梁，提升了育人实效，接下来，我校将充分利用校友资源为母校毕业生提供就业岗位，既能够使校友成为学校与企业之间的纽带，也能让毕业生服务校友企业，双方互利共赢。希望同学们脚踏实地、奋勇向前，愿同学们都能找到自己心仪的工作！</span></span></p><p><br/></p>